---
alwaysApply: true
---
1-Always explain before writing code

2-Prefer explicit typing

3-Ask questions instead of guessing

4-All code comments must be in Turkish and concise

5-All commit messages must be in Turkish and concise

6-Always separate between sections with a block comment in this format:
   <!-- ================================================ -->
   <!-- Section Title / Description -->
   <!-- ================================================ -->

7-For dynamic links (URLs), always use $this->getURL — do not hardcode or build URLs manually.

8-Use BaseURL only in the places intended for it (e.g. assets, static paths, base path contexts) — do not use it for page/route links; use $this->getURL for those.

9-To get images from the database, use $this->dbResimAl() with: (image field/data, type e.g. "urun", dimensions e.g. "400x0"). Example: $ek_resim = $this->dbResimAl($urun["ek_resim"], "urun", "400x0");

10-For every page view, always set SEO variables at the top: $sayfa (page slug), $baslik (page title), and $this->sayfaBaslik = $baslik . " - " . $this->ayarlar("title_" . $lang). Use $this->ogBaslik when the page has Open Graph meta. Example (from blog.php): $sayfa = "blog"; $baslik = "Blog"; $this->sayfaBaslik = $baslik . " - " . $this->ayarlar("title_" . $lang);

11-To fetch blog posts (and similar lang-aware lists), use $this->dbLangSelect(table, where, imageField, extra, orderBy). Example: $all_blogs = $this->dbLangSelect("blog", "aktif = 1 AND sil = 0 AND baslik <> ''", "resim", "", "ORDER BY sira DESC, id DESC");

12-To fetch the photo gallery, use $this->dbLangSelect on table "dosyalar" with type = 'galeri'. Example: $foto_galeri = $this->dbLangSelect("dosyalar", "aktif = 1 AND sil = 0 AND type = 'galeri'", "resim", "", "ORDER BY sira asc, id asc");